{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-05-20",
 "title": "Assembling a Team to Hunt the Death Star",
 "summary": "Falsely disgraced and brought in cuffs to New Republic Intelligence headquarters, the pilot Bazil McKenzie is actually there to assemble a covert team to gather intelligence on the latest Death Star. After his amused guards uncuff him, he links up with the flamboyant Twi'lek operative Xanatos, who arrives under the cover identity \"Mister Baldur\" to meet \"Mister Mackenzie.\" The NRI agent Kathryn, operating as the alias Mersche Lumbroscopic, attaches herself to the pair, revealing she has already loaded the Triton with everything known about previous Death Stars. Adopting his own false identity as the freighter owner Mege Vauki, Bazil agrees to pose as Xanatos's master to ease the Twi'lek's passage through Imperial space, and the three set off down the hall to begin their mission against a daunting enemy.",
